Laila Ali LADR5604 Ionic Soft Bonnet Dryer, Purple and White
description: Ionic soft bonnet dryer uses ion infused airflow to dry hair quickly, and is perfect for drying roller sets and braids as well as processing chemical and conditioning treatments. The ionic technology helps retain moisture to prevent breakage for shinier, healthier-looking hair styles. With 3 heat and speed settings, you have the flexibility to dry and style your hair exactly the way you want. When you are done you can use the cool setting, which releases cool air to help set the style. The purple and black adjustable soft bonnet can accommodate a set of jumbo rollers so you can create loose curls and waves quickly. The bonnet comes with a compact and convenient storage case that holds the entire unit, including the power cord.
